definition: to catch sight of in a doorway (old)

sentences.english: I walked up to the cardboard and looked at the one butterfly who he had just pinned to the large paper.

sentences.english: Gray paperboard packaging made with a variety of gift packaging to the world.
sentences.chinese: 用灰板纸做出的包装能够丰富多彩的礼品包装世界。

sentences.english: Coated White boards are of great prospect in its extensive application as quality packaging material.
sentences.chinese: 涂布白板纸作为精美包装材料具有广泛的应用前景。

sentences.english: This paper analysis the interrelationship in the three consistency circuits inthe Xin layer pulp.
sentences.chinese: 本论文结合白板纸制浆线，详细分析了浓度调节工艺。

sentences.english: The high-end gift packaging paperboard material is essential materials.
sentences.chinese: 而高档的礼品包装的材料灰板纸是必不可少的用料。
